Photo:VCGÂ Chinese President Xi Jinping on Sunday said China is willing to deepen mutually beneficial cooperation in an all-round way with Kyrgyzstan, so as to bring more benefits to the people of the two countries.Xi made the remarks when meeting with Kyrgyz President Sadyr Zhaparov who came to China for the opening ceremony of the Beijing 2022 Olympic Winter Games.Xi also said China stands ready to comprehensively upgrade security cooperation with Kyrgyzstan to jointly safeguard the security and stability of the two countries and the region.